sections.heading: Receptacle, other term, defined
sections.text: As used in sections 28-1329 to 28-1334, unless the context otherwise requires:(1) Receptacle shall mean not only bottles, siphons, tins, kegs, one-eighth barrels, quarter barrels, half barrels, barrels, boxes, ice cream cabinets, cans and tubs, but all other receptacl
